Package bauernhof.app

Class GaCo

  • java.lang.Object
    • bauernhof.app.GaCo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    bauernhof.preset.GameConfiguration
    public class GaCo
extends Object
implements bauernhof.preset.GameConfiguration
    Represents the GameConfiguration class. This class is responsible for managing the configuration of the game, including the number of deposition area slots, the number of cards per player hand, the cards and card colors, and the raw configuration.
    Since:
    2023-06-27
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    julius.hunold
